  <entry>
    <title>使用hexo搭建github个人主页 -自用极简版</title>
    <url>/2022/08/07/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BAgithub%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%B5/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、安装nodeJs"><a href="#一、安装nodeJs" class="headerlink" title="一、安装nodeJs"></a>一、安装nodeJs</h2><p>可参考官方文档 <a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/">hexo-下载</a></p>
<p>deepin 可能需要特殊处理</p>
<h2 id="二、本地关联库"><a href="#二、本地关联库" class="headerlink" title="二、本地关联库"></a>二、本地关联库</h2><h3 id="github创建同名库"><a href="#github创建同名库" class="headerlink" title="github创建同名库"></a>github创建同名库</h3><ol>
<li>使用github创建一个跟用户名同名的库，比如我的用户名是 breezehan，那么就创建一个 breezehan.github.io 的库</li>
<li>根本地文件夹关联，或者先clone<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> git@github.com:breezehan/breezehan.github.io.git my-blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ol>
<h3 id="hexo"><a href="#hexo" class="headerlink" title="hexo"></a>hexo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo init my-blog</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> my-blog</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git -save</span><br><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="根目录的-config-yml"><a href="#根目录的-config-yml" class="headerlink" title="根目录的_config.yml"></a>根目录的_config.yml</h3><p>修改主题为：<br>theme: next</p>
<h3 id="本地运行"><a href="#本地运行" class="headerlink" title="本地运行"></a>本地运行</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>查看 <a href="http://localhost:4000/">http://localhost:4000/</a> 是否正常</p>
<h3 id="部署到github"><a href="#部署到github" class="headerlink" title="部署到github"></a>部署到github</h3><p>修改根目录 _config.yml</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">repo:</span> <span class="string">git@github.com:breezehan/breezehan.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">branch:</span> <span class="string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo g -d </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<span id="more"></span> 

<h2 id="三、保存源文件"><a href="#三、保存源文件" class="headerlink" title="三、保存源文件"></a>三、保存源文件</h2><h3 id="3-1-在github上创建一个新分支，比如source，可以把主分支改为source"><a href="#3-1-在github上创建一个新分支，比如source，可以把主分支改为source" class="headerlink" title="3.1 在github上创建一个新分支，比如source，可以把主分支改为source"></a>3.1 在github上创建一个新分支，比如source，可以把主分支改为source</h3><h3 id="3-2-本地切换到source分支，修改-gitignore-，只保留source目录和根目录下的文件"><a href="#3-2-本地切换到source分支，修改-gitignore-，只保留source目录和根目录下的文件" class="headerlink" title="3.2 本地切换到source分支，修改 .gitignore ，只保留source目录和根目录下的文件"></a>3.2 本地切换到source分支，修改 .gitignore ，只保留source目录和根目录下的文件</h3><h3 id="3-3-submodules保存theme"><a href="#3-3-submodules保存theme" class="headerlink" title="3.3 submodules保存theme"></a>3.3 submodules保存theme</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git submodule add https://github.com/next-theme/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="3-4-themes-x2F-next-的-config-yml，可以在根目录中创建一个-config-next-yml等方式保存"><a href="#3-4-themes-x2F-next-的-config-yml，可以在根目录中创建一个-config-next-yml等方式保存" class="headerlink" title="3.4 themes&#x2F;next 的 _config.yml，可以在根目录中创建一个 _config.next.yml等方式保存"></a>3.4 themes&#x2F;next 的 _config.yml，可以在根目录中创建一个 _config.next.yml等方式保存</h3><h3 id="3-5-push-到-github"><a href="#3-5-push-到-github" class="headerlink" title="3.5 push 到 github"></a>3.5 push 到 github</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git add .</span><br><span class="line">$ git commit-m <span class="string">&quot;source分支保存源文件&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">$ git push origin <span class="built_in">source</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="四、异地、异机使用"><a href="#四、异地、异机使用" class="headerlink" title="四、异地、异机使用"></a>四、异地、异机使用</h2><h3 id="多级clone"><a href="#多级clone" class="headerlink" title="多级clone"></a>多级clone</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git <span class="built_in">clone</span> --recurse-submodules git@github.com:breezehan/breezehan.github.io.git my-blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="环境配置"><a href="#环境配置" class="headerlink" title="环境配置"></a>环境配置</h3><p>本地查看运行效果</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> my-blog</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git -save</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="五、标签、目录"><a href="#五、标签、目录" class="headerlink" title="五、标签、目录"></a>五、标签、目录</h2><h3 id="5-1-打开配置-themes-x2F-next-x2F-config-yml"><a href="#5-1-打开配置-themes-x2F-next-x2F-config-yml" class="headerlink" title="5.1 打开配置:themes&#x2F;next&#x2F;_config.yml"></a>5.1 打开配置:themes&#x2F;next&#x2F;_config.yml</h3><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span> </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">home:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-home</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#about: /about/ || fa fa-user</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-tags</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">/categories/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-th</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">archives:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fa</span> <span class="string">fa-archive</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#schedule: /schedule/ || fa fa-calendar</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#sitemap: /sitemap.xml || fa fa-sitemap</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#commonweal: /404/ || fa fa-heartbeat</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="5-2-新建tags-page"><a href="#5-2-新建tags-page" class="headerlink" title="5.2 新建tags page"></a>5.2 新建tags page</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>修改blog&#x2F;source&#x2F;tags&#x2F;index.md，增加一行 type: “tags”</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 标签</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-08-05 20:25:03</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;tags&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>


<h3 id="5-3-新建categories-page"><a href="#5-3-新建categories-page" class="headerlink" title="5.3 新建categories page"></a>5.3 新建categories page</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>修改blog&#x2F;source&#x2F;categories&#x2F;index.md，增加一行 type: “categories”</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 文章分类</span><br><span class="line">date: 2022-08-05 20:18:33</span><br><span class="line">type: &quot;categories&quot;</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="5-4-文章中使用"><a href="#5-4-文章中使用" class="headerlink" title="5.4 文章中使用"></a>5.4 文章中使用</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">&quot;xxxx&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>文章中添加</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: 文章的标题</span><br><span class="line">date: 发表时间，如：2021-08-15 08:15:16</span><br><span class="line">description: 摘要(非必须)。也可以这一行删去，在文章中想要截断的地方加入&lt;!--more--&gt;，这样在首页就只显示开头到截断的内容，而不会显示全文</span><br><span class="line">categories:</span><br><span class="line">- 分类</span><br><span class="line">- 子分类</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">- 标签1</span><br><span class="line">- 标签2</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="五、其他"><a href="#五、其他" class="headerlink" title="五、其他"></a>五、其他</h2><blockquote>
<p>工具使用: vscode、typora</p>
</blockquote>
]]></content>
